title: Alabama State Using Bye Week to Recover, Evaluate
text:
Alabama State Using Bye Week to Recover, Evaluate Tools By Alabama News Network 
Story Created: Oct 21, 2015 at 5:12 PM CDT 
MONTGOMERY, AL --- The Alabama State Hornets have reached the halfway point of their season and are currently enjoying a bye week. 
Even though the Hornets are not facing anyone this week, Coach Jenkins still wants his team to find ways to fix the constant mistakes they've made all year.
